{
  "stem": "11205.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't know if he's-- was killed because on the way, whoever-- you know, it was quite a lot of kilometers to make.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who was weak and who couldn't, so they shoot them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest, when-- was when they brought them to the Bug, they told them to swim.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a lot which got over, the Russians caught them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They sent them back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, we didn't know nothing about what happened to our father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But being already in Taganrog, we had a letter that my father was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he had a bullet in his leg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was-- he was injured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he fell down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He played that he's dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the whole party passed, he crawled to a farmer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the farmer came and-- later to Chelm and told my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother must probably brought him back because none of the letters we ever had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We knew that father is sick because she-- in letters, my mother used to say which doctor is coming to treat him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And most probably-- that what I think, that he died from this wound.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you know, in my yizkor book, it's all written about this march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there, there, it was already the 1st of December.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a lot of-- a lot of-- didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Taganrog, they brought us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- and they treated us very nice, which was really-- there was such a respect because we were really different than the Russian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us work, even people which nobody-- they didn't give people by profession, only where they needed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my, my brother-in-law-- that was the [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In, in Russian, that's leather-- a, a tannery.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
